rd hashes.\n- Malformed final non-empty line is tolerated as partial write.\n- Malformed middle line fails.\n- Mismatched transcript `cwd` fails.\n- Session ids are converted to hashed safe session keys.\n- Human and JSON output do not contain the full transcript path.\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-09T17:50:56.320Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}